6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to revenue and taxation; amending 68
O.S. 2021, Section 3638, as amended by Section 3,
8 Chapter 347, O.S.L. 2023 (68 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section
3638), which relates to the Filmed in Oklahoma Act of
9 2021; modifying provisions related to certain
credits; and providing an effective date.
10
11
12
13
14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 68 O.S. 2021, Section 3638, as
16 amended by Section 3, Chapter 347, O.S.L. 2023 (68 O.S. Supp. 2024,
17 Section 3638), is amended to read as follows:
18 Section 3638. All production projects for which any incentive
19 is paid pursuant to the provisions of the Filmed in Oklahoma Act of
20 2021 shall contain a logo, as approved by the Oklahoma Department of
21 Commerce, to be displayed in the credits of the finished production
22 for a period of at least five (5) seconds or at the beginning of the
23 finished production prior to the start of any scene or dialogue for
24 a period of at least three (3) seconds or, if the production does
Req. No. 11469 Page 1
1 not contain credits, the Oklahoma Department of Commerce shall
2 obtain a commitment by the production company to provide equivalent
3 value as determined by the Oklahoma Department of Commerce.
4 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
